+# Phase 7.9 — Read-Only External Probe
+
+Phase 7.9 adds a read-only external probe boundary.
+
+The phase remains fake-only. It converts an operator external review report into
+a probe request, runs a fake read-only adapter, and emits a probe result.
+
+No external service is contacted in this phase.
